{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tesserarii</strong> is a dice rolling, rogue-like strategy game all about increasing the power of your dice and winning big.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246470/extras/CrazyCombosTextInDieFont.png?t=1737074062\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the satisfying nature of Tesserarii as you watch your strategic choices roll out in front of you.  You'll need your wits about you at every turn to ensure your best chance of defeating powerful bosses, or leave your fate up to lady luck and risk it all.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246470/extras/EnemyLineup.png?t=1737074062\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't let your guard down though! Each battle requires you to best deal with the randomness of rolling dice.  Break the game through combining different powerups at the right time to ignite your dice and progress through the stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246470/extras/TestFireBackgroundRemoved00000028.gif?t=1737074062\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 100+ different powerups (with more coming soon).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Powerups to modify 17 different stats to best suit your build.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Over 50 different enemies to encounter and defeat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Infinite ways to play.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737074062","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/